{
  "stem": "24409.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember that part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the next thing I knew was that a man was putting bandages around me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a Yugoslav physician on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he bandaged me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Greeks didn't let me enter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They also didn't force me to go into Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yugoslavia wouldn't have taken me, anyhow, in this condition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was brought to the home of a farmer who lived on the border between the two countries.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a Greek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was recuperating there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't know how weak I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was very weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was given milk, very much milk, and [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] turtles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They have turtles there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They run around, the turtles, by the hundreds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I got turtle, and turtle soup, and turtle meat, which is a main in this town there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, the Irgun had learned what has happened to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't remember how I did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Bernstein came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And somehow, yes, the Irgun came and spoke to the-- spoke to the Chief Rabbi of Saloniki, that he should-- Jews were very influential in Greece.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were-- was a very powerful Jewish community in Saloniki.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I think are the largest percentage of any city in Europe of Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the Chief Rabbi said, to this criminal, who breaks the law, blatantly and brings shame upon all the Jews, no, I won't move a finger.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The same rabbi, to my very great regret, was a year, or two years later, deported, with all his community, to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, I got back again from the border, back again, to Piraeus to the jail there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was not in a real jail in Piraeus.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
